Help on skill: sharpen
Skill type: neutral
Usage duration: 10

With this skill you can make your weapon a more deadly one.
The weapon must have an edge to be sharpened.
This skill can be used to sharpen piercing weapons too
but it is less effective than with slashing weapons.

Repairing a weapon removes the effects of this skill.
Your skill percent affects how much the class of weapon
will increase.

